NSL, Next Synthesis Language, is a one of the Hardware Description Language and successor of SFL. NSL is Register Transfer Level HDL, the syntax is like C.
Please see here: http://www.ip-arch.jp/indexe.html http://www.overtone.co.jp/en/products/about_nsl/

NSL can be converted to Verilog HDL or VHDL or System C with NSL Core.
